{"tid":1432242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(人手置頂) 有關延遲顯示評分","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T08:02:10.000Z","uid":104309,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4de9eaaf031146c294d634df243397592c4abb3e","tid":1432242,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"我建議連仔將延遲顯示改成，當用户評左分，就即刻顯示評分。<br />\n<br />\n原因如下，<br />\n一旦用戶評左分，就無得更改，只要係評分前唔好顯示評分，就好難比人帶風向。<br />\n<br />\n依家延遲評分會搞到好似單機上連登，唔知主流或大眾意見，咁會引起更大分歧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e3858824770c17ce8026154c346907e1517136","tid":1432242,"uid":104309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:47:30.000Z","msg":"評分後即顯示眾人評分，其互動性更豐富<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09bbca7076046a6c2609e6464cf577cd6803443","tid":1432242,"uid":104309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"有無人支持"},{"pid":"94f5edd563eb1698e9715ceb709ceeafb81948c9","tid":1432242,"uid":104309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"單機上連登會更易比人帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967510da6fb17171cd31646f37a2eb4d0d3f0f65","tid":1432242,"uid":104309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"單機上連登會造成分化，因為個個都以為自己方向正確，難以團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e48090e3ebc4d4e8c2cd40650e714e93bfb07a7","tid":1432242,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b42d564bfc34a8fd533866e529c004a78a668a85","tid":1432242,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ecafc84395babff5d585921a7bacda01558a39c9","tid":1432242,"uid":104309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:51:35.000Z